    <title>Technical Support for Radio Stations</title>
    <description>At present, the FrontlineSMS:Radio team are developing a new platform that ‘will assist community radio stations to interact dynamically with audiences by harnessing the power of SMS text messaging’. As part of this, the team are conducting a pilot with ten radio stations or shows in Kenya, Zambia, Malawi and Sierra Leone. Indigo are pleased to announce that we have made a grant of £10,000 to FrontlineSMS to help with some of the costs incurred during the pilot phase.</description>
